snippet.title: "Tree of Savior: Neverland" Carnival Edition is Here!
snippet.description:
Embark on a Timeless Journey of Love
The Carnival Edition is here! Adventure Server Giveaway: 120 Draws + 8-piece Gold Gear Set

"Tree of Savior: Neverland" Carnival Edition is Here!
Experience the all-new Tree Bond System by hosting a romantic Tree Ceremony; 
rally your allies and prepare to face the challenge of the new Demon God Dungeon Boss!
Don't forget to log into the New Adventure Server to claim 120 free draws, 
an 8-piece gold gear set, and an exclusive 4-piece golden fashion set for free!
Let's Embark on a Timeless Journey of Love!

————————————————————————————————————
👉Link: https://bit.ly/3Pir8Jv
 #TreeOfSavior  #ToSNeverland
